dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Northern Illinois University College of Law
dmca.principal_name: Northern Illinois University College of Law

works.description:
I am the media chair for the Northern  
Illinois College of Law Trial Advocacy Society, The google group website  

was made by students several years ago to represent the  however when they
 
graduated they didn't document the login names or passwords. The content
is  
now horribly out of date and the documents posted are confusing to the  
students who are competing in our competitons. We need this google group  

taken down, or given access to it so we can bring it up to date, either  
option is fine. The students who put it up were agents of the organizaton 

at the time, but they no longer are, so this site no longer has the  
blessing of the official organization.
